backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526650\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cwh1665702866803.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cwh1665702866803.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cwh1665702866803.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cwh1665702866803\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Depending on the specific page display error symptom, here are some possible causes\n      and resolutions.</p>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__section_d905e1_d906e1_d907e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121614e49\">Symptom: Page has not refreshed, or appears to have not refreshed. </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb__entry__1\">Page in cache.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb__entry__2\">Select <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Ctrl+F5</span> (Ctrl+Refresh).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb__entry__1\">Server Page not (correctly) compiled.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb__entry__2\">Compile the Server Page and check whether errors occur.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb__entry__1\">Server Page not loaded by the Uniface Server.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_wk1_nd4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution: In the [SETTINGS] section in the Server assignment file, set\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$TEST_MODE_COMPONENTS</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__section_d908e1_d909e1_d910e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121614e113\">\n Symptom: Parts of the page, such as styles and images, are not displayed.\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_r1p_yd4_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_r1p_yd4_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_r1p_yd4_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_r1p_yd4_hwb__entry__1\">Relative paths used in the skeletons (for example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">../css\n                           /applic.css</code>) cannot be translated into absolute paths.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_r1p_yd4_hwb__entry__2\">Check whether virtual directory specified in WWW publishing service is\n                        identical to path specified in <code class=\"ph codeph\">WEBAPPURL</code> setting in URD\n                        Servlet Alias.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__section_d911e1_d912e1_d913e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121614e159\">\n Symptom: Controls are not displayed when the page is submitted after a button is pressed.\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_zmj_124_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_zmj_124_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_zmj_124_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_zmj_124_hwb__entry__1\">Non-database fields have an initial value.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_zmj_124_hwb__entry__2\">Set <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Is Static</span> property to\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section dropDown\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__section_d914e1_d915e1_d916e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d121614e205\">\n Symptom: Extra occurrence is displayed in browser after pressing button.\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_pl4_124_hwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_pl4_124_hwb__entry__1\">Possible cause</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__table_pl4_124_hwb__entry__2\">Resolution</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_pl4_124_hwb__entry__1\">Server Page is intended to display one occurrence, but synchronization\n                        results in extra occurrence.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"cwh1665702866803__table_pl4_124_hwb__entry__2\">Change <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database Behavior</span> to\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">Record</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__li_d11360e1_d11361e1_d11362e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__p_d23117e1_d23118e1_d23119e1\">\n                  Possible cause: Server Page is intended to display one occurrence, but synchronization results in extra occurrence.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cwh1665702866803__p_d23120e1_d23121e1_d23122e1\"> Resolution: Change <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database\n                     Behavior</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Record</code>. </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qsg1665702688984.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Data Access</a><p>Determines the degree to which data in the component can be edited and stored.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526650\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526650\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Server Pages are not Displayed Correctly Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Depending on the specific page display error symptom, here are some possible causes and resolutions. Symptom: Page has not refreshed, or appears to have not refreshed. Possible cause Resolution Page in cache. Select Ctrl+F5 (Ctrl+Refresh). Server Page not (correctly) compiled. Compile the Server Page and check whether errors occur. Server Page not loaded by the Uniface Server. Resolution: In the [SETTINGS] section in the Server assignment file, set $TEST_MODE_COMPONENTS . Symptom: Parts of the page, such as styles and images, are not displayed. Possible cause Resolution Relative paths used in the skeletons (for example, ../css /applic.css ) cannot be translated into absolute paths. Check whether virtual directory specified in WWW publishing service is identical to path specified in WEBAPPURL setting in URD Servlet Alias. Symptom: Controls are not displayed when the page is submitted after a button is pressed. Possible cause Resolution Non-database fields have an initial value. Set Is Static property to True . Symptom: Extra occurrence is displayed in browser after pressing button. Possible cause Resolution Server Page is intended to display one occurrence, but synchronization results in extra occurrence. Change Database Behavior to Record . Possible cause: Server Page is intended to display one occurrence, but synchronization results in extra occurrence. Resolution: Change Database Behavior to Record . Related Links Data Access Determines the degree to which data in the component can be edited and stored. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}